# TimedText:FlyGirlQueenLatifah.ogg.en.srt

1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
(desire) I know you want me
2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:4,000
(you're fine) thank you
3
00:00:4,000 --> 00:00:7,000
But I'm not the type of girl that you think I am
4
00:00:7,000 --> 00:00:9,000
I don't jump into the arms of every man
5
00:00:9,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(but I'm paid) I don't need your money
6
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,000
(I love you) you must
